set_msgout

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_msgout -  This is the method used to query the current message to use when exiting a room.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int set_msgout(string str)
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the message to print when entering a room.
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This is the method used to query the current message to use when
exiting a room.   A $N in the string will be expanded to the
name and a $T will be expanded to the to direction.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
/handlers/room_handler, query_msgout(), set_msgin()

.EP

